title: Chris Smith (New Jersey politician)
added: Smith served as [https://bioguideretro.congress.gov/Home/MemberDetails?memIndex=S000522 Chairman of the House Committee on Veterans Affair]s from 2001 to 2005, a position he used to author multiple laws including a law to address homelessness among veterans and an update to the GI Bill. Smith has also served as chairman of human rights-focused subcommittee on the House Committee on Foreign Relations and has [https://www.csce.gov/about-csce/our-structure/leadership chaired the United States Helsinki Commission].
